lead_paragraph: A federal magistrate on Tuesday ordered a Phoenix woman to remain jailed until she is returned to Las Vegas to face federal charges alleging she threw a shoe at Hillary Rodham Clinton during a speech.

headline.main: Alleged Hillary Clinton Shoe Thrower Detained
